{"tid":2197542,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同ex分開咗十幾年，但仍然經常性夢到佢。。。","createTime":"2020-09-10T16:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T09:53:23.000Z","uid":73381,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6867fd8107658b871f9750152cdc35789f362e6d","tid":2197542,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"我同ex已經分開咗十幾年 依家有個拍咗十年拖好穩定就黎會結婚嘅女朋友 <br />\n<br />\n對ex已經完全冇哂感覺 平時就算見面或者見到佢同佢男朋友嘅合照都唔會覺得點<br />\n<br />\n但依然經常性發夢都會夢到佢(一星期大概兩三次)<br />\n<br />\n內容基本上都係：<br />\n1. 做愛<br />\n2. 佢同我講其實最鍾意嘅人係我<br />\n3. 同佢好甜密出去玩或者食飯嘅場景<br />\n<br />\n係唔係因為我內心深處其實仲未放得低佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2295568c75df5b2af0e6195edb5aed126cf753e","tid":2197542,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"951b7fdc8814df9c2fdb1c8daccb94392add1573","tid":2197542,"uid":234509,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"樓主得22歲<br />\n同ex分開咗十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主小學就拍拖？"},{"pid":"d37dbf5dd2f4380f47829cd89d4003e713caa93e","tid":2197542,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95543cab2209054f812f740815cc129a39a3d4c9","tid":2197542,"uid":38189,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"951b7fdc8814df9c2fdb1c8daccb94392add1573","tid":2197542,"uid":234509,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"樓主得22歲<br />\n同ex分開咗十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主小學就拍拖？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:29:09.000Z","msg":"佢12歲就做愛 有咩問題"},{"pid":"542b61267df3edc5d0f16c612911ed50